# @COMMENT: WZATB includes a similar story in HSNXV2P294D to HSNXV2P295A in the story of the Raid on the Banū al-Muṣṭaliq and the Prophet's marriage to Jūwayrīyah bint al-Ḥārith in a narrative structure much like that found in WSFAB, WYBWS, WMSAH, WSSAA, WAMAQ, and WJHZA. WMSAH also witnessed an account completely unlike his other version and unlike other versions. The story related by WSACD is narratively different and more similar to that found in WAIYA. WBSAB produced a truncated version. WZAZA also relates the story with yet another narrative structure.

